## Goal

Use **Grok SuperGrok Heavy** (`grok-composer-2.5-fast`) inside **Cursor Agent/Composer** via a local OpenAI-compatible proxy that forwards to the Grok CLI subscription backend.

```
Cursor (cloud) â†’ https://mac.foltyn.dev/ai/v1 â†’ ai-proxy :8317 â†’ Grok CLI proxy â†’ api.x.ai
```

---

## Cursor BYOK settings (working)

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Base URL | `https://mac.foltyn.dev/ai/v1` (no trailing slash) |
| API Key | `<proxyApiKey>` |
| Model | `martin/grok/grok-composer-2.5-fast` |

Config: `~/.genesis-tools/ai-proxy/config.json` (`AiProxyConfigStore` / `AiProxyStorage`)

Public exposure config (`public` block):
```json
{
  "mode": "cloudflared",
  "hostname": "mac.foltyn.dev",
  "basePath": "/ai",
  "cloudflared": { "tunnelName": "foltyn-home", "autoStart": true }
}
```

Modes: `none` | `cloudflared` | `tailscale` | `custom` â€” tunnel is **optional** for local dev.

---

## Lifecycle commands

```bash
tools ai-proxy config              # interactive menu (+ setup-tunnel wizard)
tools ai-proxy config setup-tunnel # cloudflared / tailscale / custom
tools ai-proxy up                  # start proxy (+ tunnel if cloudflared autoStart)
tools ai-proxy down                # stop proxy ONLY (never kills cloudflared)
tools ai-proxy status
```

**Important:** `down` never stops `cloudflared` â€” dev-dashboard catch-all on `mac.foltyn.dev` stays up.

### After reboot

```bash
tools ai-proxy up
# cloudflared starts automatically if not running and public.cloudflared.autoStart=true
# If tunnel already running (shared), up leaves it alone
```

### Background state files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `~/.genesis-tools/ai-proxy/proxy.pid` | ai-proxy process |
| `~/.genesis-tools/ai-proxy/runtime.json` | proxy + tunnel metadata |
| `~/.genesis-tools/ai-proxy/proxy.log` | proxy stdout/stderr |
| `~/.genesis-tools/ai-proxy/tunnel.log` | tunnel stdout/stderr (if started by up) |

### cloudflared ingress (shared tunnel)

`~/.cloudflared/config.yml` â€” ai-proxy managed block:
```yaml
  # ai-proxy (managed by tools ai-proxy)
  - hostname: mac.foltyn.dev
    path: /ai
    service: http://127.0.0.1:8317
```

Dev-dashboard catch-all unchanged: `mac.foltyn.dev` â†’ `:3042`

